{"tid":2080692,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"標普指港版國安法不影響經濟 評級展望為「穩定」","createTime":"2020-06-26T15:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T16:26:38.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"def9696fe7a4bf2ab72871b69ad36dcf5c50679b","tid":2080692,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200626/photo/bkn-20200626185042790-0626_00842_001_01p.jpg?20200626222037\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200626%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200626185042790-0626_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20200626222037&h=f5be98f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際評級機構標普發表報告，今年本港經濟或會再次出現嚴重收縮，政府推出財政刺激措施導致赤字擴大，惟目前的財政緩衝足以吸收有關措施對信貸的影響。該投資評級機構確認予香港政府長期發行人「AA+」信用評級，及短期發行人「A+」信用評級。<br />\n<br />\n此外標普認為即將實施「港區國安法」而導致制度改變，不會影響香港根據《基本法》制定經濟政策的自主權，同時<span style=\"color: red;\">美國與香港之間貿易關係亦不會發生任何變化</span>，且不會香港的金融業發展及經濟增長造成嚴重損害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/491010/%E6%A8%99%E6%99%AE%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AFaa-%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F?itm_source=universal_search&amp;itm_campaign=hk01&amp;itm_content=all&amp;itm_medium=web\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F491010%2F%25E6%25A8%2599%25E6%2599%25AE%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AFaa-%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%25A9%2595%25E7%25B4%259A-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%3Fitm_source%3Duniversal_search%26itm_campaign%3Dhk01%26itm_content%3Dall%26itm_medium%3Dweb&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=89aea077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/491010/%E6%A8%99%E6%99%AE%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AFaa-%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F?itm_source=universal_search&amp;itm_campaign=hk01&amp;itm_content=all&amp;itm_medium=web</a>"},{"pid":"502102a522366fa31d16bc70e2b3d72a82184018","tid":2080692,"uid":10014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:09:06.000Z","msg":"過左數"},{"pid":"8c0a0d44cb15e0b71891dbc42bc99ee2daefb976","tid":2080692,"uid":33373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"def9696fe7a4bf2ab72871b69ad36dcf5c50679b","tid":2080692,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200626/photo/bkn-20200626185042790-0626_00842_001_01p.jpg?20200626222037\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200626%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200626185042790-0626_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20200626222037&h=f5be98f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際評級機構標普發表報告，今年本港經濟或會再次出現嚴重收縮，政府推出財政刺激措施導致赤字擴大，惟目前的財政緩衝足以吸收有關措施對信貸的影響。該投資評級機構確認予香港政府長期發行人「AA+」信用評級，及短期發行人「A+」信用評級。<br />\n<br />\n此外標普認為即將實施「港區國安法」而導致制度改變，不會影響香港根據《基本法》制定經濟政策的自主權，同時<span style=\"color: red;\">美國與香港之間貿易關係亦不會發生任何變化</span>，且不會香港的金融業發展及經濟增長造成嚴重損害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/491010/%E6%A8%99%E6%99%AE%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AFaa-%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F?itm_source=universal_search&amp;itm_campaign=hk01&amp;itm_content=all&amp;itm_medium=web\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F491010%2F%25E6%25A8%2599%25E6%2599%25AE%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AFaa-%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7